Group management: 1. Group owner can add remove administrators 2. Group owner administrators can add remove members directly 3. Other members can invite new members new invitations will be shown to the owner admin and wait for review 4. Owner admin can review new invitations confirm whether accept them 5. Administrator cannot quit group until the owner remove them from administrators list. DIM group is based on a consensus algorithm it s created by the founder the ID was generated in the founder s app and broadcast to its members. The relay stations intermediate nodes cannot change the member list the group owner founder controls everything.

Decentralized Group Chats: 1. Generate group ID and meta info in your device 2. Manage the membership based on a consensus algorithm 3. Send group messages after encrypted by a cipher key generated locally share this key with all members in this group only Based on the above you can completely control your group no dependence on any central server.
